{"type": "article", "id": 15982, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-13T07:51:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 17108, "name": "Nikken Cutlery"}, {"id": 17109, "name": "atmos"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 17110, "name": "akif kurtulus"}, {"id": 17111, "name": "Igor Lobanov"}, {"id": 17112, "name": "Thomas Hick"}, {"id": 17113, "name": "Verena Hennig"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135735Ilv4wWxpcrHCThb0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t Lift Up Storage System by Igor Lobanov\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这款升降挂衣杆来自俄罗斯的著名设计师 Igor Lobanov，它的外面覆盖了一面镜子，和里面的挂杆一起通过滑轮升降，就能将挂着的衣服或伞等杂物隐藏在镜子里，以保持墙面的整洁。这个设计同样适用于置物柜，柜子滑下来时，小朋友也就能取拿东西了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103013lHTJ9vQcoiAadB0g.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103013qYxSE8tMCNh3yPpj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103014v1RT2MwQglVSknhi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.39428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103015dfSLFBcEyQ1mvOMa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tFolding Lamp by Thomas Hick\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款折叠灯，原本是一块 48 厘米宽的正方形不锈钢金属片，你可以顺着折痕折叠成想要的形状，再将灯泡包进去，所以每一款灯都是独一无二的并呈现出强烈的折纸感。光线通过折叠的灯罩放射出来，改变灯罩的开合意味着调整光线的明暗，完全体现了手工自由多变的特征。这是来自比利时的设计，一共有 6 种颜色选择，近期会在 Kickstarter 出售。<a href=\"http://folding-lamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> 这里是他们的主页。 </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103015Tgb7Xky8W0nRAjEe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103015OYk5nm4hRoTBsbFS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65357143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103016DPq6I0lAntrkzVSJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103016n3S9XpgiQPe4UZo1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103017rNFj1Zw8fcoOAi2I.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tRoll collection by Verena Hennig \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自德国设计师 Verena Hennig 的椅子，包括凳子、长椅和带靠背的椅子三种。座位和靠背都是椭圆形的框架加竖条铝棒，配上两根弯曲的铝棍做腿，有简单的时尚感。它们真正的特别之处在于所有铝棒都是可滚动的，自带按摩功能，也增加了人和椅子的互动。有红、白、黑、米黄四种颜色，预计明年 1 月上市。<a href=\"http://www.hennigstore.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103017Kr6IOp3XodkcvbEB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72115385\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103018euPCLnSREZwFIghT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071030182rY0GeZOn64dqc8w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103019ZkiQKwoOF2IeC7BL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64423077\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103019FXjpd9wgOJkvirLu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70726496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t刀剪刀 by Nikken Cutlery \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这套剪刀结合了日本武士刀的样式，来自刀具制造商 Nikken Cutlery。其中一款甚至以织田信长的佩刀压切为原型，剪刀的把手印有红色柄卷，呼应刀刃处缠绕的红绳，刀柄上还有织田家的家徽，以纪念最原始的武士精神。此外，Nikken Cutlery 还推出了一款黑色的架子，将剪刀倒立放置，完全是一个装饰品。<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=sr_pg_1?rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%80%E3%81%AF%E3%81%95%E3%81%BF&amp;keywords=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%80%E3%81%AF%E3%81%95%E3%81%BF&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1443687518\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103020D2n1X50gS6Z4pmfU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103020MSkwPK6QJU9LlrmT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.19655172\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103021W3fsAgV4yT0K5c9h.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103021id0TqlrfZxP4e961.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.255\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103021fob2dBmR9UsO5IyF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72068966\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071030222UQEbRVIl1GOfMaC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.94991653\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tAutumn Night by atmos &amp; PUMA \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\tAlexander McQueen 旗下的 Puma 和日本球鞋品牌 atmos 联合推出了 Disc Blaze 鞋型的新款“Autumn Night”。在深蓝色的鞋身上点缀着亮点，营造出繁星满天或在城市中亮起斑斓灯光的景象。鞋底更使用天蓝色的夜光材质，让这款鞋成为黑暗中的亮点。<a href=\"http://www.atmos-tokyo.com/category/ATMOS/360497_01.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103022MeztONvAZrITfY0K.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75594295\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103023S5sXrmc7ENVtlp0d.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103023jCoBF43DXRkv8S7s.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.91559633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071030232lMsQURA7qd6Tf01.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98878505\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103024yJpC4w2zQhqOjo1t.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60493827\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t“E.R.A” by akif kurtulus\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可以用来生火煮食物的“E.R.A”（Emergency Relief Assistance），打开缠绕在外的束带，取出上面倒扣的炉子和下面的锅就可以用任何燃料生火了。炉子外还加了防风罩，能将锅盆固定起来。而一些必备的小工具如指南针、手电筒、小刀和急救包等都能放在中间，方便携带。适合户外野餐或者灾难来临时的不时之需。<a href=\"http://www.akifkurtulus.com/#1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103024hyXZGNc16k823t97.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103025082B43LDEymkHRPN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103025duiSEKC2J1QmFkz0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103026V7pcDnJMqxmKN3Lh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071030269WQFIfH3RCn8za4k.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73838631\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}